  "title": "Full-time Veterinary Surgeon",
  "description": "<p><em>\"Happiness does not come from doing easy work but from the afterglow of satisfaction that comes after the achievement of a difficult task that demanded our best.</em>” - Theodore Isaac Rubin<br /><br /><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>At Pets Avenue Veterinary Clinic and Referrals (PAVCAR), you will contribute to delivering exceptional veterinary care by supporting our general practice, urgent care and referral surgery services. Join a passionate team dedicated to advancing pet health and client support through collaborative, high-quality medical practice.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Deliver urgent care veterinary services during evening shifts to provide timely and effective medical interventions for pets</li><li>Collaborate with a multidisciplinary team of veterinarians and support staff to optimize patient outcomes and client satisfaction</li><li>Engage in continuous professional development activities, including in-house journal clubs and morbidity & mortality rounds, to enhance clinical knowledge and skills</li><li>Participate in mentoring and coaching programs to foster career growth and professional advancement</li><li>Support the clinic’s mission to provide compassionate care that goes beyond routine veterinary services, positively impacting pets and their owners</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Demonstrated passion for veterinary medicine and commitment to delivering high-quality care</li><li>Ability to work effectively in a team environment with veterinarians of varying experience levels and support staff</li><li>Strong communication skills to engage with pet owners and colleagues professionally and empathetically</li><li>Willingness to participate in ongoing learning and professional development initiatives</li></ul><p><strong>Other Information</strong></p><ul><li>Continuous Professional Development (CPD) support provided</li><li>Discounts available for insurance packages and other benefits</li><li>For more information, visit https://www.pavcarvets.com/</li><li>Interested candidates are invited to email ryan.pavcar@gmail.com with a cover letter and updated CV</li></ul>",
